e `done`, feature stories selected normally\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n## AC 3: In-progress non-TD wins over TD backlog\n\n**Method:** Vitest test `TD gate: in-progress non-TD beats TD backlog`\n**Evidence:** Test passes — in-progress story (Tier A) selected over TD backlog (Tier D)\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n## AC 4: Verifying non-TD wins over TD backlog\n\n**Method:** Vitest test `TD gate: verifying non-TD beats TD backlog`\n**Evidence:** Test passes — verifying story (Tier B/C) selected over TD backlog (Tier D)\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n## AC 5: No TD stories, normal backlog selection\n\n**Method:** Vitest test `TD gate: no TD, normal lex order`\n**Evidence:** Test passes — without TD stories, normal lexicographic + attempt ordering applies\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n## AC 6: TD in-progress follows Tier A priority\n\n**Method:** Vitest test `TD gate: TD in-progress = Tier A`\n**Evidence:** Test passes — TD story at in-progress uses Tier A priority, not TD gate\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n## AC 7: Build succeeds with zero errors\n\n**Method:** `npm run build`\n**Evidence:** Build success in 25ms, zero errors\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n## AC 8: All tests pass with zero regressions\n\n**Method:** `npx vitest run` + BATS\n**Evidence:** 3666 vitest tests pass (139 files), 307 BATS tests pass. Zero failures.\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n## AC 9: No modified file exceeds 300 lines\n\n**Method:** `wc -l` on modified files\n**Evidence:**\n- selector.ts: 129 lines\n- selector.test.ts: 292 lines\nBoth under 300.\n**Verdict:** PASS\n\n## Summary\n\n| AC | Verdict |\n|----|---------|\n| 1  | PASS    |\n| 2  | PASS    |\n| 3  | PASS    |\n| 4  | PASS    |\n| 5  | PASS    |\n| 6  | PASS    |\n| 7  | PASS    |\n| 8  | PASS    |\n| 9  | PASS    |\n\n**Overall: 9/9 PASS, 0 FAIL, 0 ESCALATE**\n","numLines":80,"startLine":1,"totalLines":80}}}
